<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalgam lopitak ei ngak Van khelgam achun a um hi,
 Ziechun mithiengtho kum chengin a kikhawm;
 Kin takin nite chuh a bei, Lalgam hungtun nai dingin,
 Lalgam hungtunna ding chuh a naita ie!

[V2]
 Aw Lalgam hungtunna ding a naita ie (2)
 Ka thagau kisazo in pengkun hunggi pai intin,
 Lalpen chuh, A lopina'n kilang ding.

[V3]
 2. Chunglama Lalgam lopi guotlawk chuh kinepna ahi,
 Hukdampa hung kilang ding kinepna tawh;
 Aman khawvel khatvei puksa sal apat ei tandawk tai,
 Lalgam hung tunna ding chuh a naita ie!

[V4]
 3. Lalgam hungtung chu tawh I Lalpau deihtak mel chuh mui tiu,
 Lalgam latman Lalpen kilang masa ding;
 A min chu Hallelujah, A thisana ei Tanpa chuh,
 Lalgam hungtunna ding chuh a naita ie!

[V5]
 4. Khawvel in angaksawt bektak ziekin anguizo ta ie,
 Lauthawng in mite lungle a dawng hiel tai;
 A mau chuh lalgam thu hilh hitingun lan hihhalh hitiu,
 Lalgam hungtun ding a naih takzie thu chuh.</lyrics>
<title>THE COMING OF THE KINGDOM</title>
<hymn_number>146</hymn_number>
</song>